import LogoHeaderIcon from '../../ui/LogoHeaderIcon.js'
import LogoFooterIcon from '../../ui/LogoFooterIcon.js'

const Logo = (className) => {

  return parent === 'header' 
    ? (
      <button
        data-btn="root"
        className="${parentClassName}__logo"
      >
        ${LogoHeaderIcon()}
      </button>
    )
    : `<button
        data-btn="root"
        class="${parentClassName}__logo"
      >
        ${LogoFooterIcon()}
      </button>
    `
}

export default Logo
